		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><span class="smallcaps"><strong>Michelle Cacho-Negrete</strong></span> is a retired social worker living in Wells, Maine, where she leads creative-writing workshops. She has received the Hope Award for creative nonfiction and twice been nominated for a Pushcart Prize.</p><a href="/contributors/michelle-cacho-negrete" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
